text.tspan: Quick Reference Guide to UNSC Ranks
A publication of the Office of Naval Intelligence, Division Two. Approved for public release. Funding for this publication provided in part by Misriah Armories Ltd
For those who haven't served in defense of humanity against the Covenant, the various ranks and insignai of UNSC
personnel can be confusing. This document seeks to clarify what's what, and provide some insight into the world of
the UNSC. Note that this is a general guide, as units may have altered insignia or rank names to suit their needs.
